---
title: Cheesy Buffalo Chicken Tacos with Creamy Ranch Slaw
description: Move over, Buffalo wings—there’s a new dish in town! This epic taco mashup comes together in a flash—just ten minutes, to be exact. Our secret? We start with fully-cooked chicken breasts to cut down on cook time, tossing them in a blend of melted butter and spicy Buffalo seasoning. It’s all stuffed into tortillas that are blanketed in a layer of melty pepper jack cheese, then topped with a creamy ranch slaw for a twist on the typical Buffalo dipper. It doesn’t get much better than this, folks.
